data.description: Great location and Motivated Sellers!!! This home offers 3 bedrooms 2 baths and large fenced in back yard with mature trees. Bonaventure split floor plan.  Home has been freshly painted throughout the interior. Home comes with Wayne Dalton Fabric Hurricane Panels. Maintained by terminex with On Guard bait stations. All appliances and washer and dryer conveys. Palmers Place II subdivision. NO HOA!   All information deemed reliable but not guarenteed. Buyer to verify all information deemed pertinent.
